<h1>Sliding Windows</h1>
Solar InnovationsÂ® offers thermally enhanced sliding glass windows, which are customized to meet your specific requirements. The windows can be used in either commercial or residential applications, including: patios, sunrooms, or box seats in stadiums.

All sliding windows are constructed with durable aluminum frames, which will weather very well for years to come. Rotting, warping, and constant maintenance to the finish is eliminated when you chose an aluminum window. Eight standard finishes are available to choose from, along with any custom color your specific job may require. Various wood veneer species are available for the sliding windows, including: mahogany, pine, cedar, birch, and Douglas fir. The warm wood interiors help create a traditional, inviting atmosphere.

